Chapter 5:

Switching

-Circuit Switching (1G / 2G / 3G)
-Packet Switching

Circuit Switching : Dedicated communication path between two stations


*********************************************************
Telco
1G, 2G, --- Circuit (voice transmission)
2.5, 2.75, 3G --- Circuit + Packet (keno packet switching ashlo eta bujhte hobe)
4G => Packet Switching
*********************************************************

Circuit switching:
Advantage:
- Data transfer faster
- Reduced Header Size (as routing er jonno onek kom info dorkar, karon dedicated
path)
- see slide

Disadvantage:
- No sharing
- see slide

packets need no intelligence, mane jehetu dedicated path, mane path ektai,
ejonno packet k rasta chinaite hobe na kindof...so, kom data needed

subscriber loop == local loop (amar basha theke j tar gese, and abar okhan theke
fire ashse, ei loop ta)

Packet Switching:
prefered over ciruit switching.
choto choto packet akare split hobe boro message gula, packet gula bangladesh er
router e joma hoye, onno desher router e jabe, oi desher router theke abar arek 
desher router e, and so on.